    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece Shogi is a board game that adds new rules to traditional Shogi. Players can create a variety of strategies by using pieces with special effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121530/extras/9b7230232fbd7d20f12aaad59aee8f24.avif?t=1729550735\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pieces with special effects</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Double movement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Rotate +45 degrees</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Penetrate (jumps over a friendly piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Reflect (the path of the piece is reflected by the edge of the board) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Swap (swap the position of the pieces)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Place bombs or portals</p>",
